NAME
    Business::PaperlessTrans::Client - PaperlessTrans Client object

VERSION
    version 0.001000

DESCRIPTION
    PaperlessTrans is a secure and seamless bridge between your IT
    infrastructure and the Paperless Transactions cloud. This service
    enables your organization to connect directly and securely for
    processing credit card and ACH transactions.

METHODS
  submit
            my $response = $client->submit( $request );

ACKNOWLEDGMENTS
    This code contains pieces of File::ShareDir that were directly copied
    and pasted. Thanks ot Adam Kennedy for creating it.

